Package: BTSBM
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Bradley–Terry Stochastic Block Models for Paired Comparison Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person(
        given = "Lapo",
        family = "Santi",
        email = "lapo.santi@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000")
      )
    )
Description: Implements Bayesian inference for Bradley–Terry models with a 
    Stochastic Block Model (SBM) prior on the items or players being compared. 
    Provides Gibbs-type MCMC samplers, posterior relabeling, diagnostics, and 
    visualization utilities for skill clusters and block interaction strengths. 
    Useful for applications in sports analytics, psychometrics, and ranking 
    problems with latent group structures.
